{"tid":2129392,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界立即討論 押後選舉 應對策略","createTime":"2020-07-28T14:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T15:51:59.000Z","uid":80567,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f1f7c2a95c77eec0f478b3b38d7f89a715adcd5c","tid":2129392,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:25:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">1. Twitter</span><br />\nHK01 today: 港府擬提呈人大決議，<span class=\"red\">賦予權力自動延長本屆立法會一年</span>。<br />\n所以唔使等落實，依家就上去瘋狂Retweet啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/XinqiSu/status/1288105256757297155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FXinqiSu%2Fstatus%2F1288105256757297155&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=debaf958\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FXinqiSu%2Fstatus%2F1288105256757297155&h=747d2213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/XinqiSu/status/1288105256757297155</a><br />\n記得善用hashtage 例如 #legco <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">2. 跟進工會註冊</span><br />\nNOWTV (2020.05.09): 本台發現去年六月至今，<span class=\"red\">建制背景的新工會數目比泛民背景更多，亦有多個取態不明的工會以相同地址登記。</span><br />\n職工會登記局由去年6月至今，共接獲4328宗工會申請，<span class=\"red\">四千多宗登記申請未處理</span>，未能趕及在明年行政長官選舉委員會選舉中投票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">3. 提醒出年18歲嘅人去登記做選民</span><br />\n21-25歲手足好叻仔有七成二登記<br />\n26-55歲選民登記唔夠7成<br />\n廢老登記全部過七成<br />\n<br />\n選民登記方法：<br />\n即上 <a href=\"https://hk2020.vote/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote%2F&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=c944568c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote/</a><br />\n<br />\n查閱選民身份、選區／功能組別資料有無錯誤：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=c15a0ccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><br />\n<br />\n亦要關注港共會唔會借選舉本身係今年之名，禁止來年先滿18歲嘅選民投票<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">4. 留意屋企地址有冇俾人種票</span><br />\n<br />\nHK01 (2019.09.12): 吳小姐續指，該名職員稱因應她提出家裡無林姓人士，該名林姓選民將不能繼續以她的住址，作本年度的選民登記。她又引述該職員表示，由於本年度房委會轄下屋苑的新登記選民高達14萬人，<span class=\"red\">處方難以在短時間內逐一查冊，亦只會在選舉前抽查3%至5%選民，呼籲市民如發現有陌生人以自己住址登記，應盡快聯絡處方</span>，處方會陸續要求選民遞交住址證明。<br />\n<br />\n[建制種票正仆街] 我俾人盜用地址登記呀！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1443043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1443043</a>"},{"pid":"b9ed5222a549efbb02efe0cab8ed267c7cf826dc","tid":2129392,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"2e53835afce39eb916392aa95d66d1d9bffb155d","tid":2129392,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"如果可以再報名嘅話，我地不如創造史上最大型嘅萬人DQ事件<br />\n<br />\n幾萬至十萬以上嘅人報名，以自決/脫共/獨立，甚至爭取英國/台灣按照條約收返香港等訴求<br />\n<br />\n駁佢DQ，加速進度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1430b43a9927253aa21274310f9af04af536ff1f","tid":2129392,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e53835afce39eb916392aa95d66d1d9bffb155d","tid":2129392,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"如果可以再報名嘅話，我地不如創造史上最大型嘅萬人DQ事件<br />\n<br />\n幾萬至十萬以上嘅人報名，以自決/脫共/獨立，甚至爭取英國/台灣按照條約收返香港等訴求<br />\n<br />\n駁佢DQ，加速進度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:33:23.000Z","msg":"如果有人報稱政治聯繫係共產黨&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9c4323693943043169612fb648bb5176d8d807","tid":2129392,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"f0209524da9660a447839ae814b58f15f55cbbce","tid":2129392,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc